name: OZ "Back To Basics" Album
description:
The third Album by OZ Released in January of 2009, which is quoted by OZ as "My favorite album yet." (Limited offer comes with OZ Vinyl Sticker) Track List Includes
1. Intro II
2. Break Away
3. Dim The Light
4. Hold On
5. Heavy Metal Slam (Act I)

7. With Only You
8. Hide Your Heart
9. The End
10. Epilogue

name: OZ "The First Tour" DVD
description:
This DVD package follows OZ through his first two shows in Denver at the Cervantes Masterpiece Ballroom from 2008.  This DVD also includes, photo gallery, and a sound rehearsal at Flash Global Warehouse. (Limited Offer DVD includes OZ "Back To Basics" pin)
Approx running time 120 min.
